    "body": "https://github.com/KMiri-rs/asterinas/blob/6536a367f6f966270e13bae0154f579b6292b6a1/ostd/src/lib.rs#L184\n\n```rust\nAn uncaught panic occurred: panicked at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/lib.rs:184:20:\nattempt to subtract with overflow\nerror: abnormal termination: the program aborted execution\n  --> /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/osdk/deps/test-kernel/src/lib.rs:95:5\n   |\n95 |     core::intrinsics::abort();\n   |     ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ abnormal termination occurred here\n   |\n   = note: stack backtrace:\n           0: osdk_test_kernel::panic_handler\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/osdk/deps/test-kernel/src/lib.rs:95:5: 95:30\n           1: osdk_test_kernel::__ostd_panic_handler\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/osdk/deps/test-kernel/src/lib.rs:92:1: 92:30\n           2: panic\n               at src/main.rs:28:14: 28:40\n           3: ostd::invoke_ffi_init_funcs\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/lib.rs:184:20: 184:95\n           4: ostd::init\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/lib.rs:168:5: 168:28\n           5: ostd::boot::start_kernel\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/boot/mod.rs:138:14: 138:27\n           6: ostd::arch::boot::miri_boot\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/arch/miri/boot/mod.rs:73:14: 73:28\n           7: miri_start\n               at src/main.rs:18:5: 18:34\n```",
